## folder structure

myapp/
├── cmd/
│ └── myapp/ # Entry point (main.go)
│ └── main.go
├── internal/ # Private application code
│ ├── config/ # Configuration loaders
│ ├── core/ # Core business logic
│ ├── service/ # Application services
│ ├── platform/ # Platform (OS-specific) code
│ │ ├── windows/
│ │ ├── linux/
│ │ └── darwin/ # macOS
│ └── utils/ # Utility functions
├── pkg/ # Public library code for other services (if needed)
│ └── logger/
├── api/ # API definitions or protobufs
│ ├── rest/ # REST API handlers
│ └── grpc/ # gRPC services
├── scripts/ # Build, install, run scripts
├── configs/ # Config files for different envs
├── web/ # Frontend (React, Angular, etc) if any
├── build/ # Docker, CI/CD, packaging-related
├── test/ # Test cases and test data
├── go.mod
└── go.sum

windows powershell example:
1. choose any one 
$env:APP_ENV = "development"
$env:APP_ENV = "production"
$env:APP_ENV = "test"

